description:
Emily’s throwing it back to a podcast of her live radio show in 2008. She talks about her first sex party experience along with her guide for the evening, “Captain Erotica”. They discuss sex party etiquette, why attitude and partner pairing is key, what to expect, how to overcome nervousness, and why sex parties are erotic-positive and how they actually promote more intimacy in today’s culture and society.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
